The <strong><code>AbortSignal</code></strong> interface represents a signal object that allows you to communicate with a DOM request (such as a Fetch) and abort it if required via an <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController" title="The AbortController interface represents a controller object that allows you to abort one or more DOM requests as and when desired."><code>AbortController</code></a> object.